      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is strictly recommended for those looking for a major project or a donor car for parts. It is currently not in running condition due to a seized engine and a transmission that requires a full rebuild. The exterior has sustained significant damage, including heavy rust on the quarter panels and several deep dents, while the interior shows its age with torn seats and a cracked dashboard. Please be prepared to tow this vehicle from its current location, as it is not roadworthy in its present state.",
